sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as BoardPreview
    participant Service as PostService
    participant DB as Supabase DB

    User->>UI: 페이지 접속
    activate UI
    UI->>UI: useEffect() 실행

    par 인기 게시글 로딩
        UI->>Service: listTopLikedPosts(3)
        Service->>DB: SELECT ... ORDER BY like_count DESC LIMIT 3
        DB-->>Service: Rows
        Service-->>UI: setPosts(popular)
    and 카테고리별 로딩 (Free)
        UI->>Service: listPostsByCategory("free")
        Service->>DB: SELECT ... WHERE category='free'
        DB-->>Service: Rows
        Service-->>UI: setPosts(free)
    and 카테고리별 로딩 (QnA)
        UI->>Service: listPostsByCategory("qna")
        Service->>DB: SELECT ... WHERE category='qna'
        DB-->>Service: Rows
        Service-->>UI: setPosts(qna)
    end

    UI-->>User: 전체 화면 렌더링
    deactivate UI